summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5465 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 5, Ferry's Addition, being the alley between 9th Avenue West and 10th Place West, from West Fulton Street, to West Barrett Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 69478, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
